quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  17,39,"Ibi vyose nimuri vyabindi Umuremyi wawe yakweretse mubuhizi bwayo, kandi ntushire hamwe n’Imana izindi Mana ntuze utabwe mumuriro udahera witiriwe Jahannamu bagutako umwikomo nuwirukanwa hirya nohino"
  17,40,"Mbega Umuremyi wanyu niwe yabatoreye ibibondo vy’abahungu, nawe kubwiwe yigirira ibibondo vy’ukuri mwebwe muvuga amajambo akoma komeye"
  17,41,"Kandi turamaze kuku menyesha muri iyi Qur’ani ntagatifu kugira ngo bashobore kwibuka, mugabo ntaco bibafasha mwo atari ukuyanka gusa"
  17,42,"Vuga uti:- iyo bobaye hamwe n’Imana hamwe n’izindi Mana nkuko bivugira bari kurondera iyindi nzira yoba shikana Kumana"
  17,43,Irisukuye Imana kandi iri kure n’ivyo bavuga vy’ukuba kure yivyo cane
  17,44,"Amajuru yose uko ari indwi hamwe n’Isi hamwe n’ibirimwo vyose kandi ntakintu nakimwe kiriyo atari uko kininahaza Imana nkuko bayininahaza kuvyiza vyayo vyiza, mugabo mwebwe ntimutegera ukugene ihayagizwa kwayo, mu vy’ukuri Imana n’intungane, kandi niyo ifise ikigongwe gihagije"
  17,45,Mugihe uriko urasoma iyi Qur’ani ntagatifu ni nuko twashize hagati yawewe no hagati yabamwe batemera umusi w’imperuka uruzitiro rupfutswe neza
  17,46,"Twashizeho imipfundikizo mumitima yabo kugira ngo ntibaze batahure ibiriwo no mumatwi yabo tuhashiramwo uburemere bw’ukutumva, rero mugihe uvuze Umuremyi wawe muri iyi Qur’ani ntagatifu yonyene baca bahindukiza imigongo yabo n’ishavu ryinshi cane"
  17,47,"Turazi neza impamvu z’ivyo bumviriza n’igihe bakwumviriza nigihe bongorerana n’igihe abo bahemu bahemukiye imitima yabo bavuze bati:- mwebwe ntawundi muntu mukurikira atari umuntu yarozwe"
  17,48,"Namwe nimurabe igene bakugirirako uburorero n’ukuzimira, kuri ivyo ntibashobora kuronka inzira ibashikana k’ukuri kwama"
  17,49,"Nabo bavuze bati:- mbega mugihe tuzoba turi amagufa masa nukuba ibihimba vyamaze kuba ubuvungu vungu, tuzozurwa tube ibindi biremwa bishasha"